data.description: This lovely 3/1.5 home is a solid block home with a large lot and located within 5 minutes of Lake Wales; Bok Tower; and Bok Academy School. Also, the volunteer HOA will allow access to a large lake with dock 1/2 mile away for fishing and water activities. Included is a rec center for monthly events and private parties. The yard is fenced. The roof is Metal. The home has 3 nice size bedrooms with the Master being oversized. The Living room is cozy and comfortable. The kitchen has tile floors and plenty of storage space. The large Bonus Room has enough room for whatever you wish to make it. The laundry room is located in the garage area and has ample room for storage and to keep the noise away from those watching their favorite show in the Living Room. The interior of the home is freshly painted. Also has New installed A/C handler in the attic. Other New additions include: New Electrical Panel; New Stove; and New Dishwasher!  The backyard contains these trees: Loquat; Papaya; Peach; Banana; Mango; and Lemon. Some fruit being grown are: Pineapples; Sage; Lemon Balm; Spear; Spear Chocolate Mint; and Basil.  Make that appointment to see this lovely home!
